Here&#39;s another take... It simplifies the `schedulerPrepareGapEvents` function main loop by only checking whether the `startTime` is greater than the `lastMaxEndTime`, and adding the gap accordingly.  Then, once the loop is complete, the function simply checks if there is a gap between `lastMaxEndTime` and midnight (1440 minutes).

